root: ^"Excuse me, sir. Your assistance, if you please.

^All I require are some basic medicinal herbs, and I'll bounce back swiftly.
^Any chance you know someone who can aid in this matter?
^If you could lend a hand, much appreciated.
^Apologies for the brief chat, but duty calls, and I need to recline immediately."
